# Local, per-checkout agent working notes — not meant to be published.
# See .agent-notes/00-index.md for what these are.
.agent-notes/

# No dot-prefixed folder is ever checked in to this repo (IDE project files, local agent tool
# state — .idea, .claude, .junie, .agent-notes, .vscode, .cursor, whatever comes next — none of
# it is meant to be published or pulled by anyone). Only .github/ is exempted, since its
# workflow files are real, load-bearing repo infrastructure, not local tool state.
.*/
!/.github/
!/.github/**
